title: You're a WEAK Man if You Do This [Urdu/Hindi]
selftext:
This video is a wake up call.

Nobody is going to come and change your life for you.

If this doesn't motivate you, nothing will
comments: Most of indians are weak because of malnutrition and stunting

The only weak man is a man who lets others dictate what a weak man is.

(Oh look, I created a paradox. Yippy!)

To be a strong man, you should be the one who dictates for others what a weak man is.

(I just paradoxed your paradox. Ooohh)
